{
  "stem": "5758.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later on, when I went to gymnasium at the age of 12-- I think it's 11, 12-- I experienced many, many more antisemitic attacks from children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we always-- [SIGHS] we Jews had to stick together, and we had to-- we fought them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day, I really came home full of blood in my face because I got hit by-- by another schoolboy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my parents said to me, you mustn't fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they say something, go away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, no, this isn't right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I want to-- I feel that I should really give back what they do to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the professors in the gymnasium, who was physical-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was in charge of physical exercise-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Professor Meyer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the greatest antisemite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he harassed the Jewish children if they couldn't climb up the ladder fast enough or on the rope or on-- and-- and-- and-- and jumping and-- and running and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he was the first real Nazi that I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because before Hitler came to invade it-- or no, he didn't invade-- annexed Austria, because he didn't invade it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Austrian people were quite happy to receive him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Before a year-- before he already showed us a-- a-- a party member of the Nazi Party in Vienna before-- a year before he came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say there were about 75% of Jews and 25% of Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although we were in the majority, but this is why we had these fights with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually, the-- the-- the fights were closer to-- they were a little bit older than we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
